text: Bolshoye Aksakovo () is a rural locality (a selo) in Podlesnensky Selsoviet, Sterlitamaksky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 163 as of 2010. There are 7 streets. == Geography == It is located 26 km from Sterlitamak, 5 km from Podlesnoye. == References == Category:Rural localities in Sterlitamaksky District
title: Bolshoye Aksakovo
